Package sph.vaadin.ui.videojs

Contains Vaadin based Video.js UI components and related resources.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Videojs.VjsListener
    EventListener interface for listening to client side Video.js Events delegated to and fired by a Videojs player component.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Videojs
    Videojs component is based on Video.js video player.Video.js is a free open source HTML5 video player.
    VideojsController
    VideojsPlayerController is a base class for all Videojs UI control components.
    VideojsFrame
    A container for Videojs component and its basic controllers VideojsSourceLoader, VideojsSeekToController and VideojsTimeJumper.
    VideojsSeekToController
    A controller for Videojs component.
    VideojsSourceLoader
    A controller for Videojs.setSource(String, String) component.
    VideojsState
    VideojsState object is a shared state object for VideojsState component.
    VideojsTimeJumper
    A VideojsController for Videojs component.

Package sph.vaadin.ui.videojs Description
